AIM: Using Sysinternals tools for Network Tracking and Process Monitoring 

A. Check Sysinternal tools 
Path: D ◻ SOFT ◻ msc ◻ Sysinternals 

B. Monitor Live Process 
Software Used◻ Procmon 

Click on Procmon 
Click on any process which is showing SUCCESS 
Right Click ◻ Properties 
This Page will Open which will show the properties of the event 


C. Capture RAM 
Software used◻ RAMmap

Use counts
Processes

D. Capture TCP/UDP Packets 
Software used◻ TCPview

E. Monitor Hard Disk 
Software used◻ Diskmon

F. Monitor Virtual Memory 
Software used◻ VMmap

G. Monitor Cache Memory 
Software used◻ Cacheset
